## Anti-patterns

- Importing `SvgCanvasComponent` from tool code
- Injecting `SvgManipulationService` where a narrower `*SvgPort` already exists
- Mutating the **Live tree** outside `EditorCommand` (except ephemeral preview geometry in overlay SVG)
- Hardcoding tool strip buttons instead of registry-driven descriptors

## Enforcement (DEBT-008)

| Guard | Command |
|-------|---------|
| Tools must not import `svg-canvas.component` | `npm run lint` (ESLint `no-restricted-imports` on `src/app/tools/**`) |
| Pen orchestrator must not import `SvgManipulationService` | `npm run lint` (ESLint on `pen-tool-session/**`) |
| No new `getCurrentTool() === '` / `tool === '` branches in canvas | `npm run lint:arch` (baseline **6** in `tools/check-architecture-guards.mjs`) |

When shrinking the canvas hub (DEBT-001/003), lower the baseline in `check-architecture-guards.mjs` after removing branches — never raise it to allow new debt.
